==English==

===Verb===
'''switch off'''

#{{transitive}} to [[turn]] a [[switch]] to the "off" position in order to [[stop]] or [[disable]] a device
#{{idiomatic}} to [[lose]] [[interest]], and start [[thinking]] about something else

